        <updateDate>2008-01-10T22:19:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Restoring Trust in Regulator Travel Act - Prohibits a federal agency and its employees from accepting funding for travel from a nonfederal entity if such entity has been subject to the jurisdiction of that agency within two years of the travel.<br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
